title: League of Tanks is back boys
body:
Enjoying it so far? The new masteries combined with stupid little plants [make it ridiculous](http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/153683294/201055854?tab=overview).

Double cinderhulk ganks mean a dead doggy. Can't wait to try out smite Sion.
